title: Catering Information
text: ☕ Refreshments, Tea & Coffee will be available on arrival and throughout the day. 🥪 Lunch will be available between 12:30 - 13:30. You will also have an opportunity to network. We will cater for those with specific food allergies and/or requirements.​🍕 Refreshments will be available after the event.

title: Reboot London 2025 Inclusive Briefing Pack
text: We have prepared a Reboot London Inclusive Briefing Pack which describes what you will experience at the event and includes accessibility information. A copy is stored on the Reboot London event SharePoint site and some printed copies are available at reception.

title: Wi-Fi
text: To connect to Wi-Fi use-  Network: CONVENE​ Password: stayconnected​  Please avoid connecting unnecessary devices to avoid any impact to the Hackathon.​

title: Schedule of the day
text: 🕕 08:00: Doors Open to Hackers (& Hacker Teams Can Begin)​ 🕕 08:30: General Registration Opens​ 🕕 09:00: Intro and information for hackers 🕕 09:30: Welcome Speeches & Announcements ​🕕 10:00: Tech Talks & Workshops Begin and The Hack Continues ​🕕 12:30: Lunch​🕕 13:30: The Programme Continues ​🕕 16:20: Hack Pitches Start – Pizza Party 🍕​🕕 17:40: Hackathon Winners Announced & Celebratory Refreshments​🕕 18:30: Event Closes​
